            "bilateral smoothing in flesh zones suppresses brushstroke texture; "
            "cool-pearl tint at highlights (lum > 0.74) and rose blush in midtones "
            "(0.40 < lum < 0.68) recreate his characteristic porcelain-ivory quality.  "
